            <div class="total-capacity">
                <p><b>Total Dev Capacity:</b>  <span class="final-value">@Model.totalDevCapacity</span></p>
                <p><b>Average Per Sprint: </b> <span class="final-value">@Model.avgPerSprint</span></p>
